OL,5, When his son was sent to fight in      
OL,6, Ukraine, Sergei begged him not to go.  
OL,8,F"You've got relatives there. Just      
OL,9,Frefuse," Sergei recalls telling Stas,  
OL,10,Fwho is an army officer. "But he said he
OL,11,Fwas going. He believed it was right. I 
OL,12,Ftold him that he was a zombie. And     
OL,13,Fthat, unfortunately, life would prove  
OL,14,Fthat."                                 
OL,16,FSergei and Stas are not the real names 
OL,17,Fof this father and son. We've changed  
OL,18,Fthem to protect their identities.      
OL,19,FSergei has invited us to his home to   
OL,20,Ftell us their story.                   
